title: Sample Book (USA), 1915
inscribed: Stamped on front cover is the year 1915.
description: Collection of different designs, each shown in multiple colorway. Patterns for living rooms, halls, dining rooms and bedrooms. Many are shown with matching top and bottom cut-out borders. Some have attached fabric swatch. The samples are arranged with the more expensive in the front of the book.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (USA), 1915; Distributed by S.A. Maxwell & Co. ; machine-printed, airbrushed, embossed, oatmeal paper; Overall: 72 x 46.5 x 5.5 cm (28 3/8 x 18 5/16 x 2 3/16 in.); Gift of C. R. Jones; 1976-74-1-1/178
